headline.print_headline: 5 Killed in Wrong Way Crash in Southwest Florida
headline.main: 5 Killed in Wrong Way Crash in Southwest Florida

lead_paragraph: A sport utility vehicle traveling the wrong way on a Florida interstate collided head-on with a sedan early Sunday, killing five people, including four fraternity brothers at the University of South Florida, authorities said.
